<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q11_v8" title="Q11_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En un taller de diseño se arman mosaicos usando baldosas cuadradas iguales.</p>
    <div>Cada baldosa cubre un área de <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>625</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Para saber la superficie total cubierta en centímetros cuadrados por un mosaico, se multiplica 625 por el número de baldosas.</div>
    <p>Se sabe además que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> equivale a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
    <p>¿Cuántos metros cuadrados cubre un mosaico armado con <m:math><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math> baldosas?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        300 000 000 metros cuadrados
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El área total del mosaico es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>625</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Luego, como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, no cubre 300 000 000 metros cuadrados.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">3 metros cuadrados<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Primero se calcula el área total en centímetros cuadrados: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>625</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Después se convierte a metros cuadrados usando <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        0,0625 metros cuadrados
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,0625</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> corresponde a una sola baldosa, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>625</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,0625</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero el mosaico tiene <m:math><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math> baldosas, así que el área total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,0625</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,0625</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        30 metros cuadrados
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El área total en centímetros cuadrados es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>625</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Para pasar de centímetros cuadrados a metros cuadrados se divide por <m:math><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, de modo que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, no cubre 30 metros cuadrados.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular el área total en centímetros cuadrados</strong></p>
            <p>Cada baldosa cubre <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>625</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> y el mosaico tiene <m:math><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math> baldosas.</p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>625</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>El mosaico cubre <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Convertir de centímetros cuadrados a metros cuadrados</strong></p>
            <p>Del enunciado se sabe que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Por eso, para convertir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> a metros cuadrados, se divide por <m:math><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mtext> cm²</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mtext> m²</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa que indica <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mtext> metros cuadrados</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> es la opción B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Un mosaico armado con <m:math><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math> baldosas cubre <strong>3 metros cuadrados</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>